### Get all courts
GET http://localhost:8080/api/courts?page=1&size=10

### Get court by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/courts/1

### Create new court
POST http://localhost:8080/api/courts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Supreme Court",
  "location": "New York",
  "jurisdiction": "Federal"
}

### Update court
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/courts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Supreme Court Updated",
  "location": "Washington D.C.",
  "jurisdiction": "Federal"
}

### Delete court
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/courts/1